{"tid":176142,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"回到過去or預知未來 你會點揀?","createTime":"2017-03-28T03:53:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-29T07:24:05.000Z","uid":39866,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"790149c0ea594a0f7d6babb025411496ab5dcc96","tid":176142,"uid":39866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T03:53:42.000Z","msg":"1. 預知因果<br />\n可以預知當前所有可行選擇既結果<br />\n預知時間視專注力而定<br />\n長駐只能預知一兩秒之後既果<br />\n極度專注可能可以預知到十幾秒<br />\n<br />\n2. 時間跳躍 回到過去<br />\n只能回到過去 無法空越未來<br />\n年齡身體狀況等唔會改變<br />\n可以帶物品<br />\n但穿越時間越長 可以帶既物品越少<br />\n大約係回到尋日可以帶一部iphone加衫褲咁上下<br />\n但回到一年前就連衫褲都帶唔到過去<br />\n平行時空 你會有雙重存在"},{"pid":"80230eafbb676272dd55dd8067986d92e74e560d","tid":176142,"uid":40082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T03:58:20.000Z","msg":"唔著衫都要打撚醒以前個個冇用既自己"},{"pid":"3d6012e45587cb3df1ae3745a78541229518ddd2","tid":176142,"uid":39866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T04:00:33.000Z","msg":"2.<br />\n<br />\n變性之後返去幫自己破處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5b3e06fe1bf96ac961b53423ade6a65b107e52d","tid":176142,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T04:01:16.000Z","msg":"預知未來<br />\n出門前預知交通狀況<br />\n返工就唔怕遲到"},{"pid":"18611180c323fb378ce3447a88df2c5a49ad7e3b","tid":176142,"uid":39866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T04:04:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>預知未來<br />\n出門前預知交通狀況<br />\n返工就唔怕遲到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你剩係預知到十幾秒咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eec3bc3d5b68942b1e3c3bc10c7c9cc495049db7","tid":176142,"uid":39559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T04:06:15.000Z","msg":"如果我改變左過去既我<br />\n現在既我會唔會係咪都唔會變?<br />\n<br />\n係既我要預知算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2dff12406ff51a22bd92b4d26b3b6d6380b9ec6","tid":176142,"uid":25270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite