,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T04:16:56.000Z","msg":"千其唔好要預知未來能力<br />\n<br />\n你預知到未來 但改變唔到既個種無力感會迫死你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：過來人"},{"pid":"394a489ab2a0062a50c03bcb68361532c79f55c2","tid":176142,"uid":3852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T04:17:31.000Z","msg":"過大海"},{"pid":"a29188097340839cb3bfca683e48da376bcc537c","tid":176142,"uid":39866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T04:19:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>預知同改變到係兩回事<br />\n知道10秒後發生咩事冇咩用<br />\n有意外都未必避到<br />\n一個鐘就話姐<br />\n用嚟又好炒股咩都好<br />\n回到過去買六合彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你可以預知到所以選擇既結果<br />\n你可以改變你既選擇<br />\n<br />\n所以嚴格黎講係預知因果<br />\n唔係預知未來"},{"pid":"8712ee0063f4d43ba1f71c6e7627e234e8c0c0b4","tid":176142,"uid":39866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T04:20:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>千其唔好要預知未來能力<br />\n<br />\n你預知到未來 但改變唔到既個種無力感會迫死你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：過來人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n預知到d咩"},{"pid":"92f1c89f2979d311acc47aa1aace59670d8c2b83","tid":176142,"uid":39866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T04:23:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>回到過去 中學好多野冇做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係用你呢家呢個老餅身體返去wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feacb812ff38889508deb7aef3496bb1270c345f","tid":176142,"uid":39866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T04:24:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>十幾秒夠唔夠去賭大細</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有機會夠百家樂果d"},{"pid":"6f72c94024262f42040885cf8030bdfe298b78de","tid":176142,"uid":35831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T04:31:58.000Z","msg":"回到過去瘋狂中六合彩<img src=\